    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been well-maintained, making it a reliable choice for any driver. The exterior paint retains a nice shine with only a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful use. Inside, the cabin is clean and comfortable, showing minimal wear on the upholstery and all electronic features functioning as intended. The engine starts easily and runs strong, providing a smooth driving experience that reflects its consistent service history.",
