    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in breathtaking, mint condition, presenting exactly as it did the day it was delivered from the showroom. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no signs of wear. Every mechanical and electronic component functions perfectly, reflecting the meticulous maintenance and climate-controlled storage this car has received. It is a true collector-grade example that needs nothing but a new owner who appreciates perfection.",
