    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You\u2019ve seriously got to see this beauty\u2014it\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve absolutely babied this car since day one, and it\u2019s in pristine shape inside and out. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels brand new but without that heavy new-car price tag, this is the one for you. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. Come take it for a spin; I promise you\u2019re going to love it!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
