    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, presented in flawless showroom condition. The exterior features a deep, mirror-like finish on the original factory paint, entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or imperfections. Every body panel is perfectly aligned, and the premium alloy wheels are pristine, without a single scratch or hint of curb rash. Inside, the cabin remains in 'as-new' state; the hand-stitched leather upholstery is supple with zero bolster wear, and the interior still carries a fresh factory scent. All technological features, including the navigation and premium audio system, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been stored in a climate-controlled garage and serviced exclusively by master technicians with a full paper trail of records included. The engine bay is detailed to a show-standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a perfectly preserved example, complete with all original keys, manuals, and the window sticker.",
